# FinChatBot — Part 1: React Frontend Walkthrough

## Summary

Built the complete React frontend for **FinChatBot**, an AI-powered financial assistant with 4 interaction modes, chat streaming, chart rendering, file uploads, voice input, and document export.

## Stitch Design

Created 6 design screens in Stitch project `12610157595259334099`:
1. Main App Shell (sidebar + chat layout)
2. Chat Message Area (user/AI bubbles, citations, charts)
3. File Upload Modal (drag-and-drop zone)
4. Bottom Input Bar (text, voice, attach)
5. Insights Mode (scan button + insight cards grid)
6. Agentic Mode (goal input + agent stepper)

## Architecture

| Layer | Tech |
|-------|------|
| Framework | Vite + React 19 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 (dark theme) |
| State | Zustand |
| Charts | Recharts |
| Icons | Lucide React |
| Dialogs | Radix UI |
| File Upload | react-dropzone |
| Export | jsPDF, Blob API |

