## File Structure

```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/        → AppShell, Sidebar, TopBar
│   ├── chat/          → ChatWindow, MessageBubble, CitationTag, StreamingIndicator, ChatInput
│   ├── upload/        → FileUploadModal, FileDropZone, UploadedFilesList
│   ├── charts/        → ChartRenderer (bar, line, pie, scatter)
│   ├── modes/         → SmartChatMode, DocumentAnalysisMode, InsightsMode, AgenticMode
│   └── ui/            → Button, Badge, Card, Toast
├── hooks/             → useStream, useVoiceInput, useFileUpload, useChat
├── store/             → useChatStore (Zustand)
├── utils/             → exportPDF, exportMarkdown, mockData
├── constants/         → modes
├── App.tsx
└── main.tsx
```

## Additional Features
- **Voice Input**: Web Speech API (Chrome/Edge), mic glow animation
- **PDF Export**: jsPDF with formatted title page, messages, citations
- **Markdown Export**: Structured export with footnote citations
- **Keyboard Shortcuts**: Ctrl+K focuses input, Escape closes modals
- **Responsive**: Sidebar collapses on mobile, overlay mode
- **Toast Notifications**: Success/error/info with auto-dismiss
- **Smart Auto-scroll**: Stops when user scrolls up, resumes at bottom

